{
  "name": "Validation",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>Validation</strong> 属性可返回 <strong>Validation</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例更改单元格 E5 的数据有效性验证。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Modify</span>(xlValidateList, xlValidAlertStop, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;=$A$1:$A$10&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>使用 <strong>Add</strong>方法可将数据有效性添加到某个区域并创建一个新的 <strong>Validation</strong> 对象。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例为 E5 单元格添加数据有效性验证*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> validation = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlValidateWholeNumber, xlValidAlertStop, xlBetween, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;5&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;10&quot;</span>)\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">InputTitle</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Integers&quot;</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorTitle</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Integers&quot;</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">InputMessage</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Enter an integer from five to ten&quot;</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorMessage</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;You must enter a number from five to ten&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表工作表区域的数据有效性规则。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "AlertStyle",
      "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>Add</strong> 方法设置某一区域的警告样式。如果该区域已有数据有效性检验，则可用 <strong>Modify</strong> 方法更改警告样式。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回有效性检验警告样式。<strong>XlDVAlertStyle</strong> 类型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示单元格 E5 的数据有效性检验的警告样式是否为xlValidAlertInformation。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AlertStyle</span> == xlValidAlertInformation)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上 A1 单元格的数据有效性检验的警告样式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> validation = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">switch</span> (validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AlertStyle</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">xlValidAlertInformation</span>:\n            <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;警告样式为信息图标&quot;</span>)\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">xlValidAlertStop</span>:\n            <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;警告样式为停止图标&quot;</span>)\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">xlValidAlertWarning</span>:\n            <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;警告样式为警告图标&quot;</span>)\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>)\n{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) \n    {\n    \t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> \n    {\n    \t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "ErrorMessage",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置数据有效性检验错误消息。<strong>String</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向单元格 E5 添加数据有效性验证，并指定输入信息和错误消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> validation = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlValidateWholeNumber, xlValidAlertStop, xlBetween, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;5&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;10&quot;</span>)\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">InputTitle</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Integers&quot;</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorTitle</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Integers&quot;</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">InputMessage</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Enter an integer from five to ten&quot;</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorMessage</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;You must enter a number from five to ten&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示单元格 A1 的数据有效性检验错误消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorMessage</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ErrorTitle",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置数据有效性错误对话框的标题。<strong>String</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代��<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向单元格 E5 添加数据有效性验证，并指定输入信息和错误消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> validation = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlValidateWholeNumber, xlValidAlertStop, xlBetween, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;5&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;10&quot;</span>)\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">InputTitle</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Integers&quot;</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorTitle</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Integers&quot;</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">InputMessage</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Enter an integer from five to ten&quot;</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorMessage</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;You must enter a number from five to ten&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上单元格 B1 的数据有效性验证的错误对话框的标题。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> validation = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`标题为：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${validation.ErrorTitle}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Formula1",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回与条件格式或者数据有效性相关联的值或表达式。可为常量值、字符串值、单元格引用或公式。<strong>String</strong>型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示单元格 B1 的数据有效性验证的第一部分相关联的表达式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> validation = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Formula1</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作表上单元格 B1 的数据有效性验证的第一部分相关联的表达式为“=A1”，则删除该数据有效性验证。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> validation = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Formula1</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;=A1&quot;</span>) {\n        validation.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Formula2",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回与条件格式或数据有效性验证第二部分相关联的值或表达式。仅用于数据有效性条件格式 <strong>Operator</strong> 属性为 <strong>xlBetween</strong> 或 <strong>xlNotBetween</strong>的情况。可为常量值、字符串值、单元格引用或公式。<strong>String</strong> 类型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示单元格 B2 的数据有效性验证的第二部分相关联的值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Formula2</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上单元格 B2 的数据有效性验证的第二部分相关联的值赋值给 C1 单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> validation = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Formula2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "IMEMode",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>常量</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>xlIMEModeAlpha</strong></td>\n<td>半角字母数字</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlIMEModeAlphaFull</strong></td>\n<td>全角字母数字</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlIMEModeDisable</strong></td>\n<td>禁用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlIMEModeHiragana</strong></td>\n<td>平假名</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlIMEModeKatakana</strong></td>\n<td>片假名</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlIMEModeKatakanaHalf</strong></td>\n<td>片假名（半角）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlIMEModeNoControl</strong></td>\n<td>无控制</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlIMEModeOff</strong></td>\n<td>关闭（英文模式）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlIMEModeOn</strong></td>\n<td>开启</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div><p>只有安装和选择了日文语言支持时，才可设置该属性。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置日文输入规则的说明。可以是下表列出的 <strong>XlIMEMode</strong> 常量之一。<strong>Long</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置单元格 E5 的数据有效性的输入规则。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> validation = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlValidateWholeNumber, xlValidAlertStop, xlBetween, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;5&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;10&quot;</span>)\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">InputTitle</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot; seisuuchi seisuuchi seisuuchi&quot;</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorTitle</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot; seisuuchi seisuuchi seisuuchi&quot;</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">InputMessage</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;5  kara kara 10  否 seisuu seisuu o nyuuryoku nyuuryoku shite shite kudasai kudasai kudasai kudasai .&quot;</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorMessage</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot; nyuuryoku nyuuryoku dekirunowa dekirunowa dekirunowa dekirunowa dekirunowa 5  kara kara 10  madeno madeno madeno ne desu desu .&quot;</span>\n    validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IMEMode</span> = xlIMEModeAlpha\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示单元格 E1 的数据有效性的输入规则是否为xlIMEModeNoControl。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IMEMode</span> == xlIMEModeNoControl)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "IgnoreBlank",
      "summary": "<p>当 <strong>IgnoreBlank</strong> 属性为 <strong>True</strong> 时，如果单元格为空白，或者 <strong>MinVal</strong> 或 <strong>MaxVal</strong> 属性所引用的单元格为空白，仍认为该单元格数据有效。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>如果指定区域内的数据有效性检验允许空值，则该值为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将单元格 E5 的数据有效性检验设置为允许有空值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IgnoreBlank</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上单元格 E5 的数据有效性检验是否允许有空值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> validation = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Validation</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(validation.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IgnoreBlank</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "InCellDropdown",
      "summary": "<p>如果数据有效性检验类型不是 <strong>xlValidateList</strong>，将忽略该属性。</p>\n<p>可用 <strong>Validation</strong> 对象的 <strong>Add</strong> 方法或 <strong>Modify</strong> 方法的 <em>Minimum</em> 参数来指定包含有效数据的区域。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>如果数据有效性显示含有有效取值的下拉列表，则该属性值为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
